    {
      "id": "model_note_before_run",
      "type": "note",
      "x": 444,
      "y": 1030,
      "w": 450,
      "h": 185,
      "title": "Do this before Run / 运行前做这几步",
      "text": "1. Select the Preset. 2. Check Models ready. 3. If Missing, use Check/download models. 4. Wait for Queued downloads to finish. 5. Run only after Ready. / 先选中 Preset，确认 Models ready；缺失则检查/下载，等待队列完成后再运行。",
      "style": {
        "color": "#422006",
        "background": "#fde68a",
        "font_size": 13
      },
      "source": {
        "kind": "canvas_note"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "model_note_no_spam",
      "type": "note",
      "x": 444,
      "y": 1250,
      "w": 450,
      "h": 150,
      "title": "Avoid repeated Run clicks / 不要反复点 Run",
      "text": "If models are missing, repeated Run clicks only create noise. Fix readiness first, then run once and watch the queue. / 模型缺失时反复点 Run 只会制造混乱。先解决就绪状态，再运行并查看队列。",
      "style": {
        "color": "#f8fafc",
        "background": "#92400e",
        "font_size": 13
      },
      "source": {
        "kind": "canvas_note"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "model_note_template_dependency",
      "type": "note",
      "x": 1260,
      "y": 1030,
      "w": 450,
      "h": 150,
      "title": "Templates are blueprints / 模板只是蓝图",
      "text": "Starter templates are model-free guides. Future runnable templates should mark required models on the card and remain browsable even before installation. / 新手模板是无模型引导。未来可运行模板应在卡片上标注模型依赖，并允许未安装时先浏览。",
      "style": {
        "color": "#f8fafc",
        "background": "#1d4ed8",
        "font_size": 13
      },
      "source": {
        "kind": "canvas_note"
